<i>noun</i>: 소홀 [소홀], 불찰 [불찰], 방치 [방ː치], 방임 [방ː임], 등한시 [등ː한시], 과실 [과ː실], 경시 [경시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소홀 [소홀]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness; negligence; indifference</dd><br>
<dd>중요하게 생각하지 않아 주의나 정성이 부족함.</dd><br>
<dd>A lack of care or caution about something because one does not think it is important.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불찰 [불찰]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness; negligence; fault</dd><br>
<dd>주의를 기울여 조심하지 않은 탓으로 저지른 잘못.</dd><br>
<dd>A mistake made due to lack of attention or caution.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>방치 [방ː치]</dt><br>
<dd>negligence</dd><br>
<dd>무관심하게 그대로 내버려 둠.</dd><br>
<dd>The state or quality of leaving something abandoned, unattended and ignored.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>방임 [방ː임]</dt><br>
<dd>negligence; laissez faire</dd><br>
<dd>돌보거나 간섭하지 않고 제멋대로 내버려 둠.</dd><br>
<dd>The state or quality of not caring or interfering but neglecting.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>등한시 [등ː한시]</dt><br>
<dd>negligence</dd><br>
<dd>소홀하게 보아 넘김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of paying little attention to something due to disregard.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과실 [과ː실]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fault</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 주의하지 않아서 생긴 잘못이나 실수.</dd><br>
<dd>An error or a mistake made by not paying attention to something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. negligence</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 주의하지 않아서 앞으로 일어날 일을 미리 내다보지 못한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A failure to predict the future by not paying attention to something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경시 [경시]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; negligence; disdain; slight</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상을 중요하게 보지 않고 하찮게 여김.</dd><br>
<dd>Treating someone or something with disdain.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>